aṅguttara nikāya 4
28. rāgapeyyāla
275. sammappadhānasutta
“rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā.
katame cattāro?
idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati;
uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya … pe … anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya … pe … uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati.
rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti.
dutiyaṃ.
